</head>
<body>

<!-- CURSOR -->
<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-trail" id="cursorTrail"></div>

<!-- LOADER -->
<div id="loader">
  <div class="loader-logo">Papua Documentary</div>
  <div class="loader-line"></div>
  <div class="loader-text">Memuat kisah hutan terakhir...</div>
</div>

<!-- NAVBAR -->
<nav id="navbar">
  <a href="#hero" class="nav-logo">Papua Hutan</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">Tentang</a></li>
    <li><a href="#data">Data</a></li>
    <li><a href="#causes">Penyebab</a></li>
    <li><a href="#dampak">Dampak</a></li>
    <li><a href="#timeline">Timeline</a></li>
    <li><a href="#cta">Aksi</a></li>
  </ul>
  <div class="nav-hamburger" id="hamburger">
    <span></span><span></span><span></span>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- MOBILE MENU -->
<div class="nav-mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
  <a href="#about" onclick="closeMenu()">Tentang</a>
  <a href="#data" onclick="closeMenu()">Data</a>
  <a href="#causes" onclick="closeMenu()">Penyebab</a>
  <a href="#dampak" onclick="closeMenu()">Dampak</a>
  <a href="#timeline" onclick="closeMenu()">Timeline</a>
  <a href="#cta" onclick="closeMenu()">Aksi</a>
</div>

<!-- HERO SECTION -->
<section id="hero" role="banner">
  <div class="hero-video-bg">
    <div class="forest-particles" id="forestParticles"></div>
    <svg style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;opacity:0.08" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
      <defs>
        <radialGradient id="fg1" cx="30%" cy="80%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#2d8a4e" stop-opacity="0.6"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="transparent"/></radialGradient>
        <radialGradient id="fg2" cx="70%" cy="70%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#1a5c35" stop-opacity="0.5"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="transparent"/></radialGradient>
      </defs>
      <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#fg1)"/>
      <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#fg2)"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-bar-top"></div>
  <div class="hero-content" id="heroContent">
    <span class="hero-label">🌿 Dokumenter Lingkungan · Papua</span>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Papua Sedang<br>Kehilangan<br>Hutannya</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Deforestasi mengancam hutan tropis terakhir Indonesia dan kehidupan masyarakat adat Papua yang telah menjaga bumi ini selama ribuan tahun.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#about" class="btn-primary"><span>Pelajari Lebih Lanjut</span></a>
      <a href="#data" class="btn-secondary">Lihat Data</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-indicator">
    <span class="scroll-text">Scroll</span>
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT DEFORESTATION -->
<section id="about" aria-labelledby="about-title">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="reveal-left">
        <span class="section-label">01 — Apa Itu Deforestasi?</span>
        <h2 class="section-title" id="about-title">Kehilangan yang Tak Bisa<br>Dikembalikan</h2>
        <p class="section-body">Deforestasi adalah proses penebangan dan pembersihan kawasan hutan secara masif untuk dialihfungsikan menjadi lahan pertanian, perkebunan, pertambangan, atau infrastruktur. Papua, yang menyimpan lebih dari separuh hutan tersisa Indonesia, kini menghadapi ancaman terbesar dalam sejarahnya.</p>
        <p class="section-body" style="margin-top:16px">Setiap menit, ribuan pohon ditebang. Setiap hari, spesies unik kehilangan habitatnya. Setiap tahun, masyarakat adat kehilangan tanah leluhur mereka.</p>
        <div class="cause-cards" style="margin-top:36px">
          <div class="cause-card reveal delay-1">
            <div class="cause-icon">🌴</div>
            <h4>Perkebunan Sawit</h4>
            <p>Ekspansi kelapa sawit menjadi ancaman terbesar. Ratusan ribu hektar hutan dikonversi setiap tahun.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cause-card reveal delay-2">
            <div class="cause-icon">⛏️</div>
            <h4>Pertambangan</h4>
            <p>Konsesi tambang emas, tembaga, dan batu bara membuka kawasan hutan yang sebelumnya terisolasi.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cause-card reveal delay-3">
            <div class="cause-icon">🌾</div>
            <h4>Food Estate</h4>
            <p>Program lumbung pangan skala mega mengancam hutan basah dan lahan gambut Papua.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cause-card reveal delay-4">
            <div class="cause-icon">🏗️</div>
            <h4>Infrastruktur</h4>
            <p>Pembangunan jalan dan kawasan industri membuka akses ke wilayah hutan terdalam.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal-right delay-2">
        <div class="about-visual">
          <div class="about-visual-inner"></div>
          <svg style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;opacity:0.5" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
            <!-- Forest silhouette -->
            <defs>
              <linearGradient id="treeGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#2d8a4e"/>
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0a2e1a"/>
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>
            <!-- Trees left -->
            <polygon points="40,350 70,200 100,350" fill="url(#treeGrad)"/>
            <polygon points="60,350 100,160 140,350" fill="#1a5c35"/>
            <polygon points="120,350 155,190 190,350" fill="url(#treeGrad)"/>
            <polygon points="0,350 30,220 60,350" fill="#0f3d22"/>
            <!-- Trees right -->
            <polygon points="280,350 310,180 340,350" fill="url(#treeGrad)"/>
            <polygon points="310,350 345,150 380,350" fill="#1a5c35"/>
            <polygon points="350,350 385,200 420,350" fill="url(#treeGrad)"/>
            <!-- Ground -->
            <rect x="0" y="340" width="500" height="160" fill="#1a0a05" opacity="0.7"/>
            <!-- Mist -->
            <ellipse cx="200" cy="300" rx="200" ry="40" fill="rgba(200,220,200,0.06)"/>
            <ellipse cx="200" cy="280" rx="160" ry="30" fill="rgba(200,220,200,0.04)"/>
          </svg>
          <div class="about-badge">
            <div class="about-badge-num">42M+</div>
            <div class="about-badge-label">Hektare hutan Papua yang tersisa</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DATA & FAKTA -->
<section id="data" aria-labelledby="data-title">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="data-header reveal">
      <span class="section-label">02 — Data & Fakta</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="data-title">Angka yang<br>Berbicara Keras</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-card reveal delay-1">
        <div class="stat-num" data-target="15" data-suffix="Jt">0</div>
        <div class="stat-unit">Hektare</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Total hutan hilang dari seluruh Papua sejak era industrialisasi</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card reveal delay-2">
        <div class="stat-num" data-target="1" data-decimal="true" data-suffix="Jt">0</div>
        <div class="stat-unit">Hektare</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Kawasan hutan dilepas untuk kepentingan korporasi</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card reveal delay-3">
        <div class="stat-num" data-target="168471" data-suffix="">0</div>
        <div class="stat-unit">Hektare</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Hutan dikonversi menjadi perkebunan sawit aktif</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="infographic reveal">
      <div>
        <span class="section-label">Proporsi Hilang</span>
        <h3 class="infographic-label">Perbandingan<br>Tutupan Hutan</h3>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px">Dalam dua dekade terakhir, Papua kehilangan tutupan hutan dengan laju yang mengkhawatirkan. Tanpa intervensi serius, separuh hutan Papua bisa hilang pada 2050.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-bars">
        <div class="progress-item">
          <div class="progress-name"><span>Hutan Primer Tersisa</span><span>62%</span></div>
          <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" data-width="62"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-item">
          <div class="progress-name"><span>Area Terancam Deforestasi</span><span>28%</span></div>
          <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill red" data-width="28"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-item">
          <div class="progress-name"><span>Konsesi Aktif di Kawasan Hutan</span><span>45%</span></div>
          <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill red" data-width="45"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-item">
          <div class="progress-name"><span>Kawasan Terlindungi Efektif</span><span>35%</span></div>
          <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" data-width="35"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-item">
          <div class="progress-name"><span>Lahan Adat yang Diakui</span><span>18%</span></div>
          <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" data-width="18"></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PENYEBAB (Horizontal Storytelling) -->
<section id="causes">
  <div class="causes-title-section">
    <span class="section-label reveal">03 — Penyebab Utama</span>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Siapa yang<br>Menghancurkan Hutan?</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="causes-scroll">
    <div class="cause-panel reveal">
      <div class="cause-panel-bg sawit">
        <svg style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;opacity:0.15" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
          <pattern id="palmPattern" x="0" y="0" width="60" height="80" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <path d="M30,70 L30,30 M30,30 Q20,15 5,20 M30,30 Q40,15 55,20 M30,30 Q15,20 10,5 M30,30 Q45,20 50,5" stroke="#2d8a4e" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
          </pattern>
          <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#palmPattern)"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="cause-panel-overlay"></div>
      <div class="cause-panel-content">
        <div class="cause-num">01</div>
        <div class="cause-tag">Ancaman Utama</div>
        <h3>Perkebunan<br>Kelapa Sawit</h3>
        <p>Ekspansi perkebunan sawit telah menghancurkan ratusan ribu hektar hutan Papua. Perusahaan-perusahaan besar mendapat konsesi dengan proses perizinan yang tidak transparan.</p>
        <div class="cause-stat">168.471 ha<small>hutan dikonversi jadi sawit</small></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cause-panel reveal delay-2">
      <div class="cause-panel-bg food">
        <svg style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;opacity:0.1" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
          <pattern id="gridPat" x="0" y="0" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <rect x="0" y="0" width="40" height="40" fill="none" stroke="#a05a2c" stroke-width="0.5"/>
          </pattern>
          <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#gridPat)"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="cause-panel-overlay"></div>
      <div class="cause-panel-content">
        <div class="cause-num">02</div>
        <div class="cause-tag">Program Pemerintah</div>
        <h3>Food Estate<br>Papua</h3>
        <p>Program lumbung pangan nasional dirancang tanpa konsultasi masyarakat adat. Jutaan hektare hutan gambut dan hutan hujan tropis terancam dikonversi.</p>
        <div class="cause-stat">1,2 Jt ha<small>target lahan food estate Papua</small></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cause-panel reveal delay-3">
      <div class="cause-panel-bg tambang">
        <svg style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;opacity:0.12" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
          <pattern id="hexPat" x="0" y="0" width="50" height="43" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <polygon points="25,2 48,14 48,39 25,51 2,39 2,14" fill="none" stroke="#6b3a8e" stroke-width="0.8"/>
          </pattern>
          <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#hexPat)"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="cause-panel-overlay"></div>
      <div class="cause-panel-content">
        <div class="cause-num">03</div>
        <div class="cause-tag">Industri Ekstraktif</div>
        <h3>Pertambangan<br>Skala Besar</h3>
        <p>Freeport, Grasberg, dan puluhan konsesi tambang lainnya telah menciptakan kerusakan ekologis yang masif dan meninggalkan limbah beracun di sungai-sungai Papua.</p>
        <div class="cause-stat">7,3 Jt ha<small>total konsesi tambang di Papua</small></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DAMPAK -->
<section id="dampak">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="dampak-header">
      <span class="section-label reveal">04 — Dampak Nyata</span>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Konsekuensi yang<br>Menghantam Semua</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="dampak-grid">
      <div class="dampak-card reveal delay-1">
        <span class="dampak-icon">🦜</span>
        <h3>Hilangnya Habitat Satwa</h3>
        <p>Cenderawasih, kanguru pohon, dan ratusan spesies endemik Papua kehilangan rumah mereka. Papua menyimpan 30% spesies burung unik dunia yang kini terancam punah.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="dampak-card danger reveal delay-2">
        <span class="dampak-icon">🌡️</span>
        <h3>Krisis Iklim</h3>
        <p>Hutan Papua menyimpan 7,7 miliar ton karbon. Deforestasi melepas karbon masif ke atmosfer, memperparah pemanasan global yang mengancam seluruh umat manusia.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="dampak-card danger reveal delay-3">
        <span class="dampak-icon">⚖️</span>
        <h3>Konflik Tanah Adat</h3>
        <p>Ribuan warga adat menghadapi penggusuran paksa dari tanah leluhur tanpa kompensasi layak. Konflik agraria terus meningkat di seluruh wilayah Papua.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="dampak-card reveal delay-4">
        <span class="dampak-icon">🏺</span>
        <h3>Ancaman Budaya</h3>
        <p>Lebih dari 300 suku adat Papua memiliki ikatan spiritual dengan hutan. Ketika hutan hilang, tradisi, bahasa, dan pengetahuan lokal turut terancam punah.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="dampak-card danger reveal delay-5">
        <span class="dampak-icon">🌊</span>
        <h3>Banjir dan Longsor</h3>
        <p>Pembabatan hutan menghilangkan fungsi perlindungan DAS. Banjir bandang dan longsor semakin sering terjadi, menghancurkan permukiman dan lahan pertanian rakyat.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="dampak-card reveal delay-1">
        <span class="dampak-icon">💧</span>
        <h3>Pencemaran Air</h3>
        <p>Limbah tambang dan perkebunan mencemari ratusan sungai di Papua yang menjadi sumber kehidupan masyarakat. Air bersih semakin sulit didapat.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MASYARAKAT ADAT -->
<section id="masyarakat" aria-label="Masyarakat Adat Papua">
  <div class="masyarakat-visual">
    <div class="papua-pattern"></div>
    <div class="masyarakat-art"></div>
    <svg style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;z-index:0" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
      <defs>
        <radialGradient id="adatGlow" cx="50%" cy="50%">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#2d8a4e" stop-opacity="0.3"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="transparent"/>
        </radialGradient>
      </defs>
      <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#adatGlow)"/>
      <!-- Abstract tribal patterns -->
      <g opacity="0.15" stroke="#3fba6b" stroke-width="1" fill="none">
        <circle cx="50%" cy="50%" r="100"/>
        <circle cx="50%" cy="50%" r="140"/>
        <circle cx="50%" cy="50%" r="180"/>
        <path d="M 200 200 Q 250 150 300 200 Q 350 250 400 200"/>
        <path d="M 100 300 L 150 250 L 200 300 L 250 250 L 300 300"/>
      </g>
      <!-- Silhouette of person with raised hands -->
      <g transform="translate(50%, 60%)" opacity="0.2">
        <ellipse cx="0" cy="-120" rx="30" ry="35" fill="#3fba6b"/>
        <path d="M-25,-85 L-25,0 L25,0 L25,-85" fill="#3fba6b"/>
        <path d="M-25,-60 L-80,-30 M25,-60 L80,-30" stroke="#3fba6b" stroke-width="12" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </g>
    </svg>
    <div class="masyarakat-visual-overlay"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="masyarakat-content">
    <span class="section-label reveal">05 — Suara Masyarakat Adat</span>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Penjaga Hutan<br>yang Dilupakan</h2>
    <div class="blockquote reveal">
      <p>"Hutan adalah rumah dan warisan bagi generasi kami. Ketika hutan hilang, kami kehilangan diri kami sendiri."</p>
      <cite>— Tokoh Adat Suku Mee, Papua Tengah</cite>
    </div>
    <p class="section-body reveal delay-2">Lebih dari 300 suku adat di Papua telah menjaga ekosistem hutan selama ribuan tahun menggunakan kearifan lokal yang teruji. Mereka bukan hambatan pembangunan — mereka adalah solusi nyata untuk krisis iklim global.</p>
    <p class="section-body reveal delay-3" style="margin-top:16px">Namun suara mereka diabaikan dalam setiap proses pengambilan keputusan. Tanah leluhur diklaim tanpa persetujuan. Hutan spiritual ditebangi tanpa ampun.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TIMELINE -->
<section id="timeline">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="timeline-header">
      <span class="section-label reveal">06 — Kronologi</span>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Timeline<br>Kehancuran</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline-line">
      <div class="timeline-item reveal">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-year">2000</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Era Otonomi & Ekspansi Korporasi</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">Otonomi khusus Papua diberlakukan. Konsesi perkebunan sawit dan tambang mulai masuk secara besar-besaran. Deforestasi meningkat tajam setelah era reformasi.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item danger reveal delay-1">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-year">2011–2019</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Puncak Kehilangan Hutan</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">Papua kehilangan lebih dari 500.000 hektar hutan primer. Greenpeace melaporkan 168.471 hektar hutan berubah jadi kebun sawit. Konflik adat meningkat drastis.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item reveal delay-2">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-year">2021</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Proyek Food Estate Dimulai</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">Program Food Estate di Merauke dan Sorong dimulai. Jutaan hektar hutan dan lahan gambut masuk dalam target konversi. Protes keras dari masyarakat adat dan NGO lingkungan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item danger reveal delay-3">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-year">2024</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Peringatan Darurat Iklim</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">Laporan CIFOR dan Forest Watch Indonesia: laju deforestasi Papua meningkat 40% dari dekade sebelumnya. Hampir 1 juta hektar kawasan hutan dilepaskan dari status perlindungan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item danger reveal delay-4">
        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-year">2025–2026</div>
          <div class="timeline-title">Krisis yang Terus Berlanjut</div>
          <p class="timeline-desc">Ekspansi infrastruktur dan konsesi baru terus membuka hutan Papua. Masyarakat internasional mulai menekan Indonesia untuk moratorium deforestasi yang lebih kuat dan terverifikasi.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- BEFORE AFTER SLIDER -->
<section id="comparison">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="comparison-header">
      <span class="section-label reveal">07 — Perbandingan Visual</span>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Sebelum & Sesudah<br>Penebangan</h2>
      <p class="section-body reveal delay-1" style="margin:0 auto;text-align:center;max-width:500px">Geser slider untuk melihat perubahan dramatis tutupan hutan Papua sebelum dan sesudah deforestasi masif.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ba-slider-wrap reveal">
      <div class="ba-slider" id="baSlider">
        <!-- BEFORE (healthy forest) -->
        <div class="ba-after">
          <div class="ba-after-bg"></div>
          <svg style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
            <defs>
              <linearGradient id="skyG" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#0a2e1a"/>
                <stop offset="60%" stop-color="#1a5c35"/>
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0f3d22"/>
              </linearGradient>
              <linearGradient id="treeG2" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#2d8a4e"/>
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0a2e1a"/>
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#skyG)"/>
            <!-- Dense canopy -->
            <ellipse cx="100" cy="200" rx="120" ry="90" fill="#1a5c35"/>
            <ellipse cx="200" cy="180" rx="110" ry="85" fill="#2d8a4e"/>
            <ellipse cx="300" cy="195" rx="130" ry="95" fill="#1a5c35"/>
            <ellipse cx="420" cy="185" rx="115" ry="88" fill="#2d8a4e"/>
            <ellipse cx="550" cy="200" rx="125" ry="92" fill="#1a5c35"/>
            <ellipse cx="680" cy="188" rx="118" ry="88" fill="#2d8a4e"/>
            <ellipse cx="800" cy="205" rx="120" ry="92" fill="#1a5c35"/>
            <!-- Layer 2 -->
            <ellipse cx="50" cy="280" rx="100" ry="75" fill="#0f3d22"/>
            <ellipse cx="160" cy="265" rx="115" ry="78" fill="#1a5c35"/>
            <ellipse cx="280" cy="275" rx="120" ry="80" fill="#0f3d22"/>
            <ellipse cx="400" cy="268" rx="110" ry="76" fill="#1a5c35"/>
            <ellipse cx="520" cy="278" rx="118" ry="79" fill="#0f3d22"/>
            <ellipse cx="650" cy="270" rx="113" ry="77" fill="#1a5c35"/>
            <ellipse cx="780" cy="280" rx="120" ry="80" fill="#0f3d22"/>
            <!-- Ground -->
            <rect x="0" y="380" width="900" height="120" fill="#0a2e1a"/>
            <!-- Mist layer -->
            <rect x="0" y="330" width="900" height="60" fill="rgba(220,240,225,0.04)"/>
            <!-- River -->
            <path d="M 0 420 Q 200 410 400 425 Q 600 440 900 415" stroke="#1a5c9e" stroke-width="8" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="ba-label left">🌳 HUTAN ASLI</span>
        </div>
        <!-- AFTER (deforested) -->
        <div class="ba-clip" style="width:50%" id="baClip">
          <div class="ba-before">
            <div class="ba-before-bg"></div>
            <svg style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:900px;height:100%;min-width:100%" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
              <defs>
                <linearGradient id="burnG" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#5a3010"/>
                  <stop offset="50%" stop-color="#8b4513"/>
                  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#3d1a08"/>
                </linearGradient>
              </defs>
              <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#burnG)"/>
              <!-- Barren land -->
              <rect x="0" y="300" width="900" height="200" fill="#3d2010"/>
              <!-- Bare stumps -->
              <rect x="60" y="260" width="20" height="50" fill="#2d1508" rx="2"/>
              <rect x="150" y="250" width="18" height="55" fill="#2d1508" rx="2"/>
              <rect x="240" y="255" width="22" height="50" fill="#2d1508" rx="2"/>
              <rect x="350" y="248" width="20" height="57" fill="#2d1508" rx="2"/>
              <rect x="450" y="258" width="19" height="48" fill="#2d1508" rx="2"/>
              <rect x="560" y="252" width="21" height="53" fill="#2d1508" rx="2"/>
              <rect x="660" y="260" width="18" height="50" fill="#2d1508" rx="2"/>
              <rect x="760" y="255" width="22" height="52" fill="#2d1508" rx="2"/>
              <!-- Palm plantation rows -->
              <g opacity="0.6">
                <line x1="0" y1="350" x2="900" y2="350" stroke="#5a3520" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="0" y1="380" x2="900" y2="380" stroke="#5a3520" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="0" y1="410" x2="900" y2="410" stroke="#5a3520" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="100" y1="300" x2="100" y2="500" stroke="#5a3520" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="200" y1="300" x2="200" y2="500" stroke="#5a3520" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="300" y1="300" x2="300" y2="500" stroke="#5a3520" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="400" y1="300" x2="400" y2="500" stroke="#5a3520" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="500" y1="300" x2="500" y2="500" stroke="#5a3520" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="600" y1="300" x2="600" y2="500" stroke="#5a3520" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="700" y1="300" x2="700" y2="500" stroke="#5a3520" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="800" y1="300" x2="800" y2="500" stroke="#5a3520" stroke-width="1"/>
              </g>
              <!-- Smoke/haze -->
              <rect x="0" y="200" width="900" height="100" fill="rgba(180,100,50,0.08)"/>
              <!-- Hazy sky -->
              <rect x="0" y="0" width="900" height="260" fill="rgba(120,80,40,0.15)"/>
            </svg>
            <span class="ba-label right" style="right:24px">🪵 PASCA PENEBANGAN</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- DIVIDER -->
        <div class="ba-divider" id="baDivider">
          <div class="ba-handle">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2.5">
              <path d="M8 5l-5 7 5 7M16 5l5 7-5 7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- LIVE COUNTER -->
<section id="live-counter" aria-label="Penghitung Real-time Hutan Hilang">
  <div class="pulse-ring"></div>
  <div class="pulse-ring"></div>
  <div class="pulse-ring"></div>
  <div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:1;text-align:center">
    <span class="section-label reveal" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)">Live Simulation</span>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal" style="margin-bottom:0">Hutan Hilang Saat Ini</h2>
    <div class="counter-display" id="liveCounter">0</div>
    <div class="counter-sub">Hektare Hutan Hilang Sejak Anda Membuka Halaman Ini</div>
    <div class="counter-note reveal delay-2">Simulasi berdasarkan rata-rata laju deforestasi hutan Papua sekitar 0,5–1 hektar per menit. Data aktual mengacu pada laporan CIFOR dan Forest Watch Indonesia.</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INTERACTIVE MAP -->
<section id="map">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="map-header">
      <span class="section-label reveal">08 — Peta Interaktif</span>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal">Sebaran Kerusakan<br>di Papua</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="map-container reveal">
      <div class="map-svg-wrap">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 900 500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;display:block;background:#0a1a1a">
          <!-- Ocean -->
          <rect width="900" height="500" fill="#0a1520"/>
          <!-- Papua island - rough shape -->
          <path d="M 80,250 Q 100,180 140,160 Q 180,140 230,130 Q 270,120 310,125 Q 350,130 380,120 Q 420,110 460,115 Q 500,120 540,110 Q 580,100 620,108 Q 660,116 700,120 Q 740,124 780,135 Q 820,146 840,165 Q 860,184 855,210 Q 850,236 835,255 Q 820,274 800,285 Q 780,296 750,300 Q 720,304 690,300 Q 660,296 630,305 Q 600,314 570,320 Q 540,326 510,320 Q 480,314 450,325 Q 420,336 390,330 Q 360,324 330,340 Q 300,356 270,360 Q 240,364 210,355 Q 180,346 160,330 Q 140,314 120,295 Q 100,276 80,250 Z" fill="#0f3d22" stroke="#1a5c35" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <!-- Manokwari area -->
          <circle class="map-zone glow-green" cx="200" cy="175" r="18" fill="rgba(45,138,78,0.5)" stroke="#3fba6b" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <!-- Sorong area - sawit zone -->
          <ellipse class="map-zone glow-red" cx="130" cy="225" rx="35" ry="25" fill="rgba(192,57,43,0.4)" stroke="#e74c3c" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <!-- Merauke - food estate -->
          <ellipse class="map-zone glow-red" cx="790" cy="290" rx="50" ry="35" fill="rgba(192,57,43,0.45)" stroke="#e74c3c" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <!-- Freeport Grasberg -->
          <circle class="map-zone" cx="600" cy="270" r="22" fill="rgba(243,156,18,0.5)" stroke="#f39c12" stroke-width="1.5" style="animation: glowGold 2s ease infinite alternate"/>
          <!-- Bintuni Bay -->
          <ellipse class="map-zone glow-red" cx="240" cy="240" rx="30" ry="20" fill="rgba(192,57,43,0.35)" stroke="#c0392b" stroke-width="1"/>
          <!-- Wasior -->
          <circle class="map-zone glow-green" cx="310" cy="188" r="12" fill="rgba(45,138,78,0.4)" stroke="#3fba6b" stroke-width="1"/>
          <!-- Cyclops mountains -->
          <circle class="map-zone glow-green" cx="470" cy="155" r="15" fill="rgba(45,138,78,0.45)" stroke="#3fba6b" stroke-width="1.2"/>
          <!-- Mamberamo -->
          <ellipse class="map-zone glow-green" cx="540" cy="170" rx="40" ry="22" fill="rgba(45,138,78,0.3)" stroke="#2d8a4e" stroke-width="1"/>
          <!-- Lorentz NP -->
          <ellipse class="map-zone glow-green" cx="650" cy="220" rx="45" ry="30" fill="rgba(45,138,78,0.35)" stroke="#3fba6b" stroke-width="1.2"/>
          <!-- Labels -->
          <text x="130" y="270" font-family="Poppins,sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="rgba(231,76,60,0.9)" text-anchor="middle">Sorong</text>
          <text x="200" y="155" font-family="Poppins,sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="rgba(63,186,107,0.9)" text-anchor="middle">Manokwari</text>
          <text x="790" y="340" font-family="Poppins,sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="rgba(231,76,60,0.9)" text-anchor="middle">Merauke</text>
          <text x="600" y="300" font-family="Poppins,sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="rgba(243,156,18,0.9)" text-anchor="middle">Freeport</text>
          <text x="650" y="268" font-family="Poppins,sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="rgba(63,186,107,0.8)" text-anchor="middle">Lorentz NP</text>
          <text x="540" y="205" font-family="Poppins,sans-serif" font-size="10" fill="rgba(63,186,107,0.8)" text-anchor="middle">Mamberamo</text>
          <!-- Ocean label -->
          <text x="50" y="460" font-family="Poppins,sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="rgba(100,150,200,0.5)" font-style="italic">Laut Banda</text>
          <text x="800" y="460" font-family="Poppins,sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="rgba(100,150,200,0.5)" font-style="italic" text-anchor="end">Laut Arafura</text>
          <text x="450" y="50" font-family="Poppins,sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="rgba(100,150,200,0.5)" font-style="italic" text-anchor="middle">Samudera Pasifik</text>
          <!-- Grid lines for oceanographic feel -->
          <g opacity="0.05" stroke="#4a8fa8" stroke-width="0.5">
            <line x1="0" y1="100" x2="900" y2="100"/>
            <line x1="0" y1="200" x2="900" y2="200"/>
            <line x1="0" y1="300" x2="900" y2="300"/>
            <line x1="0" y1="400" x2="900" y2="400"/>
            <line x1="150" y1="0" x2="150" y2="500"/>
            <line x1="300" y1="0" x2="300" y2="500"/>
            <line x1="450" y1="0" x2="450" y2="500"/>
            <line x1="600" y1="0" x2="600" y2="500"/>
            <line x1="750" y1="0" x2="750" y2="500"/>
          </g>
          <!-- PAPUA label -->
          <text x="450" y="235" font-family="Montserrat,sans-serif" font-size="20" fill="rgba(240,237,232,0.12)" font-weight="900" text-anchor="middle" letter-spacing="8">PAPUA</text>
        </svg>
        <div class="map-legend">
          <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-white);margin-bottom:10px">Legenda</div>
          <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot deforestasi"></div>Zona Deforestasi</div>
          <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot sawit"></div>Kawasan Lindung</div>
          <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot tambang"></div>Area Pertambangan</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

